      "content": "but putting it like that just makes it feel more clinical... more like i'm a problem to be solved. it doesn't change the fact that the world is just so loud and exhausting and everything feels so temporary anyway. like i'm just waiting for the inevitable end so i don't have to keep pretending to care about any of this.",
